}}'''刘承俊'''（英語：Steve Seung Jun Yoo，韩語：유승준，{{bd|1976年|12月15日||}}）<ref>{{Cite web|title=유승준 소개|url=http://www.mnet.com/artist/863/profile|accessdate=2017-12-25|work=Mnet|language=ko|archive-date=2018-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180924070603/http://www.mnet.com/artist/863/profile|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TW0kviOrjao ‘병역 회피’ 유승준, 강제 추방] {{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TW0kviOrjao |date=20201220045316 }}, [[韓國廣播公司|韓國廣播公司]] News</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Fighting to be able to return home : After enlistment scandal, Steve Yoo is battling to come back to Korea|url=http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=3029767|accessdate=2018-09-24|author=Cho|date=February 13, 2017|first=Jin-hyung|work=Korea JoongAng Daily|archive-date=2018-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180722125814/http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aId=3029767|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是韩裔美籍歌手和演员，1997年出道后成为韩国最受欢迎的[[韓國流行音樂|K-pop]]歌手之一<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20150520001128&ACE_SEARCH=1|title=[Newsmaker] Steve Yoo asks to be taken back|author=Lee|first=Sun-young|date=2015-05-20|work=The Korea Herald|accessdate=2018-09-24|author2=Yoon|first2=Sarah|archive-date=2018-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180924105745/http://www.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20150520001128&ACE_SEARCH=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2002年，劉承俊被指責為逃避[[大韓民國徵兵制|韩国义务兵役]]而成为[[美国公民|美国公民]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Steve Yoo sues over Korea visa rejection|url=http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=3011728|accessdate=2017-12-25|author=Sung|date=November 19, 2015|first=So-young|work=Korea JoongAng Daily|archive-date=2019-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190201013445/http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aId=3011728|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他在韓國的演藝生涯就此结束。随后，他被禁止进入韩国，成为韓國历史上唯一一个因取得他国國籍而被禁止入境的人<ref name="ban">{{Cite news|url=http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/news/2015/11/18/0200000000AEN20151118006700315.html|title=Singer Yoo Seung-jun protests lifetime entry ban|date=2015-11-18|work=Yonhap News Agency|accessdate=2017-12-25|language=en|archive-date=2017-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171225202953/http://english.yonhapnews.co.kr/news/2015/11/18/0200000000AEN20151118006700315.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此后劉承俊的演藝事業轉向中国<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2017/02/24/2017022401057.html?related_all|title=Korean-American Singer Stays Barred Over Draft Dodging|author=Yang|first=Eun-kyoung|date=2017-02-24|work=The Chosun Ilbo|accessdate=2017-12-25|language=en|archive-date=2020-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200121041108/http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2017/02/24/2017022401057.html?related_all|dead-url=no}}</ref>。劉承俊的岳父去世後，他曾試圖返回韓國奔喪，但遭到韓國海關驅逐。2015年5月，劉承俊在[[香港|香港]]接受媒體採訪時在鏡頭前下跪道歉，希望韓國社會原諒他並讓允許其返回韓國，但韓國當局依舊拒絕其入境<ref>{{Cite web|title=劉承俊逃兵13年下跪道歉|url=https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20150521000847-260112?chdtv|accessdate=|author=中國時報|date=|format=|publisher=|language=}}</ref>。當時已定居在北京，直到2019年11月15日才上訴得直，允許他回到韓國。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Court rules in favor of singer banned from visiting S. Korea|url=https://en.yna.co.kr/view/AEN20191115006500315|accessdate=2020-12-31|date=2019-11-15|last=이민지|work=Yonhap News Agency|language=en|archive-date=2019-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191115062820/https://en.yna.co.kr/view/AEN20191115006500315|dead-url=no}}</ref>

